Well, just like any story...
If the characters do something stupid and unrelated to what they are doing or who they are, then it breaks the flow of the story and becomes distracting, which can become a domino effect of what happens next making the story not very interesting or really irritating to read.
Thus making it a bad story.

Or, if events that occur have no reason to occur other than lame boring writing and "I need thing to happen, so let's make something explode" or create conflict between characters for no reason other than to pad time and space, then this could also lead to bad and boringly written stories.
